# Google Identity Services — public OAuth client ID for the SPA.
# This value is NOT a secret (it ships in the frontend); the real protection is
# restricting authorized JavaScript origins in the Google Cloud Console.
# There is NO client secret: this is a public PKCE client.
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your own value.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
